latestPosts.caption:
ik this post is a little late , but today i just wanted to freeze this tiny moment forever 🕊️

i hit 1k a few days back and now we’re already close to 2k?? like WHAT!!!!!
from posting random reels with 8 views to people actually showing up for me... i can’t even explain what this means 💗

this journey feels like a cute inside joke between me and the universe.
and to the two people who made this day extra special! i love you both more than i’ll ever post about 🫶🌷

thank you for every comment, every save, every lil message.
from here on, it’s just us. building something raw, messy, and real 💌
